did.unittitle: International Association of Machinists and Aerospace Workers, Lodge 751E records
did.abstract: Records of the Association Association of Machinists and Aerospace Workers, Lodge 751E which is comprised of skilled electronics workers at Boeing.

bioghist.p: IAM 751-E is local lodge of the International Association of Machinists, District 751. Chartered by the District in 1961, the local's membership is comprised of skilled electronics workers at Boeing.

scopecontent.p: Financial and membership reports, meeting minutes, correspondence, rosters.

phystech.p: Records stored off site; advance notice required for use.

userestrict.p: Creator's literary rights transferred to the University of Washington Libraries.
